{"tid":1225872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家目標唔係林鄭下台。係一哥!!!","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T09:29:59.000Z","uid":227788,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ead47e1fec7b365d082430d804a0be2b4276813","tid":1225872,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"林鄭可能好快做多2個月就腳痛下台。<br />\n就算冇。佢做多七年。其他係好:<br />\n佢再冇能力推修例 同埋23條。我地安穩多七年。<br />\n<br />\n大家而家除左focus要 撤回修例外。<br />\n最重要係要<br />\n1. 一哥收返暴動定性 (特首講左係警務處定性, 佢只係認同) <br />\n-如果收返暴動定性。就可以救返好多義士<br />\n<br />\n2. 成立獨立調查委員會。 當中要有退休大法官。去調查612 警方 濫用暴力"},{"pid":"632172f1bbb19276c6818b94dc22bae4a2bdfc13","tid":1225872,"uid":50663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:54:04.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"2405d52696e6c76d6fcbab680f5519dd85800c4c","tid":1225872,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"both, 但首要係救人"},{"pid":"9aee4d3e9db93ac9c0d7d332449c5d06e3f775a5","tid":1225872,"uid":104833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:55:39.000Z","msg":"推，救人優先"},{"pid":"0af3a7f770eff6cc74d2ee189c767636a37ceee8","tid":1225872,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2405d52696e6c76d6fcbab680f5519dd85800c4c","tid":1225872,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:55:06.000Z","msg":"both, 但首要係救人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"真。<br />\n救義士首要任務"},{"pid":"6fc6ed900ed66aefb1a8d546a45b8045efc99acf","tid":1225872,"uid":222269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae28e1b62cd5af1c8a41c55962246ba9718ca17c","tid":1225872,"uid":261343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:57:17.000Z","msg":"林鄭擺明會報復，你睇佢調左立法會議案就會估到"},{"pid":"733f2fc2f2e34e3ca8ce40eebe4182d600109c91","tid":1225872,"uid":57206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite